Package: linkeR
Title: Link Interactive Plots and Tables in Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jake", "Wagoner", , "jakew@sci.utah.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-5053-2281"))
Description: Provides a simple interface to create bidirectional links between 
    interactive plots and tables in Shiny applications. Supports linking between
    Leaflet maps, DT tables, and other interactive components through a unified
    registry system.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
